          <name>LOG_BACKEND_EVT_PROCESS_THREAD_DONE</name>
          <briefdescription>
<para>Event when process thread finishes processing. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>This event is emitted when the process thread finishes processing pending log messages.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>This is not emitted when there are no pending log messages being processed.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Deferred mode only. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
